johto.name: Johto Safari Zone
johto.description: The Safari Zone in Johto is located on Route 48 west of Cianwood City. It features 12 unique areas with different Pokemon depending on the objects placed and time spent.

sinnoh.name: Great Marsh
sinnoh.description: The Great Marsh is Sinnoh's Safari Zone, located in Pastoria City. It costs 500 Pokedollars to enter and you receive 30 Safari Balls. Carnivine, Skorupi, and Croagunk rotate daily across the 6 areas on a 7-day cycle tied to in-game days.

kanto.name: Kanto Safari Zone
kanto.description: The Safari Zone in Kanto is located east of Fuchsia City. It offers 30 Safari Balls to catch Pokemon across multiple areas with different terrain types including grassland and water.

hoenn.name: Hoenn Safari Zone
hoenn.description: The Hoenn Safari Zone is located in the northeast area of Hoenn. It features 6 unique areas with different Pokemon accessible through various methods including grass encounters, surfing, and fishing. The catch / flee rates for Hoenn are not published, so exact numbers are not available.
